-- Schaeuble Recovering From Paralysis-Related Ailment, Finance Ministry Says
-- B y   P a t r i c k   D o n a h u e
-- 2010-10-13T12:03:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/schaeuble-recovering-from-paralysis-related-ailment-finance-ministry-says.html
German Finance Minister Wolfgang
Schaeuble’s healing process is “going well,” ministry
spokesman Michael Offer told reporters today in Berlin. The
minister is recovering from an ailment related to his paralysis.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
